569
00:32:40,170 --> 00:32:41,450
I shouldn't have done that.

570
00:32:41,800 --> 00:32:43,690
I should've really listened to you.

571
00:32:44,010 --> 00:32:45,010
Why did I lie to her

572
00:32:45,010 --> 00:32:46,170
about the baby?

573
00:32:46,800 --> 00:32:48,280
What's done is done.

574
00:32:48,410 --> 00:32:49,560
Right now,

575
00:32:49,560 --> 00:32:51,360
we must think of a way
to bring Mom back.

576
00:32:52,560 --> 00:32:54,450
It's all my fault.

577
00:32:55,782 --> 00:32:56,890
What are you talking about?

578
00:32:57,490 --> 00:32:59,250
It's my fault, too.

579
00:33:00,048 --> 00:33:00,730
I'll go with you

580
00:33:00,730 --> 00:33:02,360
to bring Mom back.

581
00:33:03,730 --> 00:33:05,210
But have you thought about it?

582
00:33:05,890 --> 00:33:06,800
If the three of us

583
00:33:06,800 --> 00:33:08,930
live together,

584
00:33:09,360 --> 00:33:10,650
there will still be conflicts.

585
00:33:11,800 --> 00:33:12,930
We're a family.

586
00:33:13,690 --> 00:33:15,650
It's on us this time.

587
00:33:15,970 --> 00:33:17,360
We can't break Mom's heart.

588
00:33:40,410 --> 00:33:41,040
Tang Xin.

589
00:34:00,800 --> 00:34:01,840
What's so urgent?

590
00:34:01,840 --> 00:34:03,115
You suddenly asked me out here.

591
00:34:04,760 --> 00:34:05,650
Let's sit and talk.

592
00:34:14,240 --> 00:34:15,010
Here's the thing.

593
00:34:15,810 --> 00:34:17,410
While I was abroad,

594
00:34:17,970 --> 00:34:19,160
someone emailed

595
00:34:19,160 --> 00:34:20,970
my informant.

596
00:34:22,810 --> 00:34:24,640
This person claimed to be my friend

597
00:34:24,770 --> 00:34:26,490
and said I was overseas,

598
00:34:26,493 --> 00:34:28,399
and asked the informant
to send them the lead

599
00:34:28,400 --> 00:34:29,490
to investigate on my behalf.

600
00:34:29,720 --> 00:34:31,240
They even tried to meet my informant.

601
00:34:32,240 --> 00:34:33,640
In that case,

602
00:34:33,770 --> 00:34:35,520
did your informant verify it?

603
00:34:35,930 --> 00:34:36,930
He sent me an email,

604
00:34:36,930 --> 00:34:38,582
but I didn't see it while I was abroad.

605
00:34:38,626 --> 00:34:40,010
I only saw it a few days ago.

606
00:34:43,240 --> 00:34:44,520
Try to recall.

607
00:34:44,770 --> 00:34:46,200
When you were writing him emails,

608
00:34:46,490 --> 00:34:48,240
did anyone see them?

609
00:34:48,850 --> 00:34:49,520
Impossible.

610
00:34:50,040 --> 00:34:51,290
I never let anyone see

611
00:34:51,290 --> 00:34:53,010
something that important,

612
00:34:53,080 --> 00:34:54,770
or told anyone his email address.

613
00:34:55,240 --> 00:34:56,560
You once mentioned

614
00:34:56,770 --> 00:34:58,160
someone used your laptop

615
00:34:58,160 --> 00:34:59,240
and changed your IP address.

616
00:34:59,770 --> 00:35:01,330
If your suspicions are correct,

617
00:35:01,330 --> 00:35:02,010
that person

618
00:35:02,010 --> 00:35:03,410
definitely knows his email.

619
00:35:05,810 --> 00:35:06,930
Other than that,

620
00:35:07,248 --> 00:35:09,248
I really can't think of
who else it could be.

621
00:35:09,330 --> 00:35:11,490
They claimed to be your friend
and tried to meet him.

622
00:35:11,680 --> 00:35:12,970
Obviously, they're using you

623
00:35:12,970 --> 00:35:14,290
to bait the informant.

624
00:35:15,200 --> 00:35:16,330
That's what I think too.

625
00:35:18,160 --> 00:35:20,040
I really want to find out who they are.

626
00:35:21,160 --> 00:35:22,450
But I'm also worried

627
00:35:22,515 --> 00:35:23,982
my informant might be in danger.

628
00:35:25,200 --> 00:35:26,770
That's why I'm asking your advice.

629
00:35:27,450 --> 00:35:29,490
Should we meet the person or not?

630
00:35:31,448 --> 00:35:32,330
Here's what we'll do.

631
00:35:33,200 --> 00:35:34,680
Tell your informant

632
00:35:34,810 --> 00:35:35,770
that if the person

633
00:35:35,770 --> 00:35:37,200
wants to meet again,

634
00:35:37,200 --> 00:35:38,240
agree to it.

635
00:35:38,850 --> 00:35:40,770
Suggest a time this weekend,

636
00:35:40,850 --> 00:35:41,930
but don't confirm

637
00:35:41,930 --> 00:35:42,960
the time or place yet.

638
00:35:43,450 --> 00:35:44,040
Wait for me.

639
00:35:44,970 --> 00:35:46,040
I'll go with you.

640
00:35:50,240 --> 00:35:50,810
All right.

641
00:35:51,290 --> 00:35:52,160
Let's do it that way.

642
00:35:54,680 --> 00:35:55,640
We need to find out

643
00:35:55,640 --> 00:35:56,810
who this person really is.

644
00:35:59,160 --> 00:35:59,770
By the way,

645
00:36:00,490 --> 00:36:01,770
ask your informant

646
00:36:01,770 --> 00:36:03,520
to forward the person's email.

647
00:36:04,720 --> 00:36:05,290
Understood.

648
00:36:22,640 --> 00:36:23,850
I have to head back now.

649
00:36:27,010 --> 00:36:27,970
That fast?

650
00:36:36,520 --> 00:36:37,240
Well, then.

651
00:36:39,010 --> 00:36:40,010
Um...

652
00:36:41,240 --> 00:36:42,520
Take care of yourself.

653
00:36:53,160 --> 00:36:54,490
All right, Mr. Chen. No problem.

654
00:36:55,450 --> 00:36:56,450
Okay. This Sunday.

655
00:36:56,450 --> 00:36:58,010
See you then.

656
00:36:58,720 --> 00:36:59,490
Okay.

657
00:37:00,160 --> 00:37:00,850
Bye.

658
00:37:04,040 --> 00:37:04,770
Mr. Han.

659
00:37:05,680 --> 00:37:07,330
Miss Tang's back from abroad.

660
00:37:07,490 --> 00:37:08,490
She's returned to work.

661
00:37:09,970 --> 00:37:10,970
Okay. Got it.

662
00:37:45,330 --> 00:37:46,490
(Miss Tang's back.)

663
00:37:46,490 --> 00:37:47,560
(When are you free)

664
00:37:47,560 --> 00:37:48,640
(to meet?)

665
00:37:58,080 --> 00:37:59,240
(Maybe this Sunday.)

666
00:38:07,490 --> 00:38:09,640
(What time and where?)

667
00:38:16,290 --> 00:38:18,640
(I'll let you know one hour before.)

668
00:38:24,860 --> 00:38:26,300
(Meeting Room)

669
00:38:27,720 --> 00:38:28,330
Mr. Tian.

670
00:38:28,330 --> 00:38:29,520
(Minghua News)

671
00:38:29,520 --> 00:38:31,240
Xin, someone's here to see you.

672
00:38:31,640 --> 00:38:33,290
I'm in a meeting. Tell them to wait.

673
00:38:35,450 --> 00:38:36,240
It's Han Yuhang.

674
00:38:41,080 --> 00:38:41,930
Mr. Han.

675
00:38:42,490 --> 00:38:43,410
What brings you here?

676
00:38:44,137 --> 00:38:45,582
I didn't make an appointment.

677
00:38:45,582 --> 00:38:46,850
I know this is sudden,

678
00:38:46,850 --> 00:38:49,160
but there's something very important

679
00:38:49,160 --> 00:38:50,330
I must tell you in person.

680
00:38:51,450 --> 00:38:52,720
What is it that's so urgent?

681
00:38:55,290 --> 00:38:56,560
While you were abroad,

682
00:38:56,560 --> 00:38:58,010
I contacted the man

683
00:38:58,010 --> 00:38:58,770
who gave you

684
00:38:58,770 --> 00:39:00,930
the sunken ship tip

685
00:39:00,930 --> 00:39:01,720
as your friend.

686
00:39:02,715 --> 00:39:04,240
How did you get in touch with him?

687
00:39:04,490 --> 00:39:05,330
The same way you did.

688
00:39:05,330 --> 00:39:06,160
Through email.

689
00:39:06,160 --> 00:39:06,770
How do you have

690
00:39:07,160 --> 00:39:08,520
his email?

691
00:39:08,680 --> 00:39:09,490
Do you know him?

692
00:39:09,770 --> 00:39:10,490
I don't know him,

693
00:39:10,490 --> 00:39:12,160
but I have my ways.

694
00:39:12,160 --> 00:39:13,010
In what ways?

695
00:39:13,290 --> 00:39:14,330
That's not important.

696
00:39:14,330 --> 00:39:16,226
What matters is that I've arranged
to meet him

697
00:39:16,248 --> 00:39:17,450
as soon as possible.

698
00:39:18,010 --> 00:39:18,640
He agreed?

699
00:39:18,640 --> 00:39:19,330
He did.

700
00:39:19,520 --> 00:39:20,810
It's this Sunday.

701
00:39:20,930 --> 00:39:22,640
The exact time and place

702
00:39:22,640 --> 00:39:24,240
will be confirmed one hour before.

703
00:39:24,240 --> 00:39:24,930
But

704
00:39:25,490 --> 00:39:26,490
he has one condition.

705
00:39:26,970 --> 00:39:28,010
When he comes to meet me,

706
00:39:28,490 --> 00:39:29,520
you have to be there.

707
00:39:34,290 --> 00:39:35,330
I'll ask you again.

708
00:39:36,520 --> 00:39:38,560
How did you get his email?

709
00:39:40,490 --> 00:39:41,970
I'm sorry.

710
00:39:42,680 --> 00:39:43,770
I can't tell you yet.

711
00:39:43,810 --> 00:39:45,040
But please believe me,

712
00:39:45,490 --> 00:39:46,720
I'm just trying to help.

713
00:39:46,850 --> 00:39:47,680
That's all.

714
00:40:32,770 --> 00:40:33,450
Mr. Han,

715
00:40:33,720 --> 00:40:36,200
you have lunch with Mr. Chan

716
00:40:36,404 --> 00:40:37,970
at the Exhibition Center Hotel at noon.

717
00:40:38,648 --> 00:40:40,720
As for the afternoon,
there's a meeting at 1:30 PM.

718
00:40:40,720 --> 00:40:41,890
You're chairing it.

719
00:40:41,890 --> 00:40:43,970
- (One hour later, Rainbow Park.)
- And tonight...

720
00:41:08,890 --> 00:41:09,680
Mr. Han.

721
00:41:10,680 --> 00:41:11,370
You're here.

722
00:41:11,970 --> 00:41:13,160
I got held up on the road.

723
00:41:13,290 --> 00:41:13,970
It's fine.

724
00:41:15,240 --> 00:41:17,010
Where are you two meeting?

725
00:41:17,490 --> 00:41:18,490
He didn't say.

726
00:41:18,490 --> 00:41:20,410
He told me to send him an email

727
00:41:20,410 --> 00:41:21,490
once we're both here.

728
00:41:21,490 --> 00:41:22,850
Then he'll tell me the exact spot.

729
00:41:22,850 --> 00:41:23,640
One sec.

730
00:41:23,720 --> 00:41:24,200
Sure.

731
00:41:24,200 --> 00:41:25,200
(Miss Tang is here.)

732
00:41:25,450 --> 00:41:26,580
(Where should we meet?)

733
00:41:28,826 --> 00:41:29,890
Let's wait for his reply.

734
00:41:35,260 --> 00:41:37,740
(You Are Under Surveillance)

735
00:42:05,381 --> 00:42:08,861
♪The vast sky and sea,
this deep blue expanse♪

736
00:42:09,551 --> 00:42:12,821
♪So deep, so boundless♪

737
00:42:13,161 --> 00:42:16,331
♪Just like your arms♪

738
00:42:16,821 --> 00:42:19,941
♪Shielding me from the dark clouds♪

739
00:42:20,231 --> 00:42:23,871
♪Always bearing it all in silence♪

740
00:42:23,871 --> 00:42:30,291
♪Even the long, long road gives me peace
when you're there♪

741
00:42:30,791 --> 00:42:35,191
♪Not one to show romance
in front of others♪

742
00:42:35,651 --> 00:42:38,741
♪You speak of dreams
with such calm simplicity♪

743
00:42:39,531 --> 00:42:44,331
♪But I know your heart
holds much deeper hopes♪

744
00:42:46,601 --> 00:42:48,441
♪I truly understand♪

745
00:42:48,931 --> 00:42:53,121
♪You speak of love so slowly♪

746
00:42:53,371 --> 00:42:59,341
♪But your eyes have already
told me everything♪

747
00:42:59,847 --> 00:43:02,537
♪Using up all my fortune♪

748
00:43:02,541 --> 00:43:06,941
♪Just to trade a lifetime with you♪

749
00:43:07,031 --> 00:43:09,251
♪Thank you for awakening♪

750
00:43:09,261 --> 00:43:14,341
♪The courage once hidden in my fear♪

751
00:43:14,481 --> 00:43:17,671
♪Turning every chance into certainty♪

752
00:43:18,001 --> 00:43:21,531
♪Turning every tie into companionship♪

753
00:43:21,611 --> 00:43:26,581
♪Blooming into brilliance
for all the years to come♪

754
00:43:26,581 --> 00:43:30,571
♪No one can tear us apart♪

755
00:43:30,761 --> 00:43:34,111
♪Each time my palm feels warmth again♪

756
00:43:34,371 --> 00:43:39,711
♪The memories return,
and I'm no longer alone♪

757
00:43:40,601 --> 00:43:44,591
♪No matter how far
across time and space♪

758
00:43:44,841 --> 00:43:48,241
♪My longing reaches you in silence♪

759
00:43:48,361 --> 00:43:52,891
♪No need to call out loudly♪

760
00:43:52,891 --> 00:43:55,561
♪No matter how much it takes♪

761
00:43:55,581 --> 00:43:59,991
♪To bring this drifting heart to shore♪

762
00:43:59,991 --> 00:44:03,251
♪Thank you for standing behind me♪

763
00:44:03,271 --> 00:44:07,321
♪Lighting up the darkness and despair♪

764
00:44:07,321 --> 00:44:10,791
♪The bigger the world,
the lonelier it feels♪

765
00:44:10,791 --> 00:44:14,561
♪Only by your side♪

766
00:44:14,571 --> 00:44:21,651
♪Can I truly feel this warmth inside♪
